beautiful things for him.

776
01:25:21,991 --> 01:25:25,324
Come on, you ass!

777
01:25:40,243 --> 01:25:41,540
Where's Stepan?

778
01:25:44,247 --> 01:25:46,442
Where did Stepan gallop to?

779
01:25:47,183 --> 01:25:49,344
He went to Zvenigorod
with the others.

780
01:25:57,226 --> 01:25:59,456
