781
01:26:16,946 --> 01:26:20,848
We'll build another mansion just
as good for the Prince's brother.

782
01:26:21,784 --> 01:26:24,116
Will the stone be better there?

783
01:26:24,921 --> 01:26:26,320
Yes, it will.

784
01:26:27,457 --> 01:26:29,482
Look, the Captain of the Guard.

785
01:26:39,469 --> 01:26:40,834
Hold on, old man.

786
01:27:24,547 --> 01:27:28,074
You, ass! Help him! In the bushes!

787
01:27:39,061 --> 01:27:40,460
Where's my whip?

788
