842
01:36:50,296 --> 01:36:54,858
THE RAID
Autumn of 1408

843
01:37:14,687 --> 01:37:18,453
They are coming! The
Tatars are coming, Prince!

844
01:38:07,173 --> 01:38:09,937
Hey, Prince! Is this your ford?

845
01:38:10,844 --> 01:38:15,076
It has been raining, and
everything is flooded. Follow us.

846
01:38:45,044 --> 01:38:47,911
We were just going to leave.
We expected you yesterday.

847
01:38:48,715 --> 01:38:53,618
I couldn't resist attacking
a small town on my way.

848
01:38:53,753 --> 01:38:54,742
I am sorry I am late.

849
01:38:54,921 --> 01:38:57,788
Never mind. Let's go. It will be
shallow to the left. Keep to the left.

850
01:39:02,562 --> 01:39:04,757
This isn't a trap?

851
01:39:05,131 --> 01:39:07,122
Believe me, Vladimir is deserted.

852
01:39:07,267 --> 01:39:10,202
My brother, the Grand
Prince, is in Lithuania.

853
01:39:10,370 --> 01:39:12,395
Here is the town, behind that forest.

854
01:39:13,039 --> 01:39:16,805
They say the Prince has a
son, but you want the throne.

855
01:39:18,344 --> 01:39:19,709
We'll see.

856
01:39:21,114 --> 01:39:24,083
I see you want the
throne. I understand.

857
01:39:29,822 --> 01:39:31,414
You were told to keep left.

858
01:39:37,597 --> 01:39:38,757
Grab this!

859
01:41:13,526 --> 01:41:16,017
Come on, Prince! Don't lag behind!

860
01:41:27,974 --> 01:41:29,532
Strong is your love for your brother.

861
01:41:29,909 --> 01:41:31,570
This is our destiny.

862
01:41:32,578 --> 01:41:34,341
When were you last
reconciled with him?

863
01:41:34,747 --> 01:41:38,148
I never was. The
Metropolitan summoned us...

864
01:41:39,952 --> 01:41:42,420
...and made us kiss the cross
and swear to live in harmony.

865
01:41:42,488 --> 01:41:43,477
What are you saying?

866
01:41:43,556 --> 01:41:45,490
The Metropolitan
summoned us to kiss the cross.

867
01:41:45,558 --> 01:41:47,719
- When?
- Last winter.

868
01:42:42,482 --> 01:42:44,814
Vladimir is a beautiful town.

869
01:42:44,884 --> 01:42:46,010
Do you like it?

870
01:42:55,962 --> 01:42:57,361
Let's go.

871
01:43:41,641 --> 01:43:45,475
Forward! You dog,
stay close, or I'll kill you!

872
01:43:47,113 --> 01:43:50,514
Keep close to the
Prince! To the gates!

873
01:44:43,469 --> 01:44:45,198
Tatars!

874
01:44:45,972 --> 01:44:47,940
Run away!

